{"tid":1860872,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港關口 = 內地權貴春袋","createTime":"2020-02-04T02:07:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T11:45:37.000Z","uid":194298,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"801f4ac652a3db2a62ba38dc50085ee34e330343","tid":1860872,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:07:27.000Z","msg":"今次事件正正將依個春袋表露無遺<br />\n陸路民用關口可以封<br />\n但內地權貴走佬路線係絕不能掂<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">深圳上榜富豪合計總財富接近1.5萬億元，超過北京全國第一</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>深圳灣</strong> -  中港車入境香港乘客連車都唔駛落，直接駛過關，直達機場<br />\n<strong>港豬澳</strong> -  澳門珠海香港直入機場島，隨時轉機走佬<br />\n<br />\n封唔封得，已經唔單單係雜種話事，而係深圳班老虎一早已經落曬ORDER<br />\n加埋其他各地領導權貴，已經執好曬行李隨時行依條線準備走佬去外國<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港，渣緊春袋<br />\n醫護罷工，封關救港</strong><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"75d9efde4a26f62e97a455fd0032904ab95d0715","tid":1860872,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:10:59.000Z","msg":"應該一早走撚晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a916a452c3fbcc70707110bf07a660ee33075541","tid":1860872,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:12:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">遲下起碼屯門至赤鱲角連接路，成條路線更加清楚便利(唔係便你班蟻民呀)</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HLTvZrX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHLTvZrX.jpg&h=df23992d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d0e8f5fbd09b0f84fac3589aac06713947fb173","tid":1860872,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75d9efde4a26f62e97a455fd0032904ab95d0715","tid":1860872,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:10:59.000Z","msg":"應該一早走撚晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:12:32.000Z","msg":"梗係未啦，而家走，轉頭無事抄硬你家，班有錢佬一定等到最後一刻先走"},{"pid":"870816c30fce9e108162f33df32ccadd6d1bf7bf","tid":1860872,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:16:55.000Z","msg":"住北京上海，都仲要先飛黎香港<br />\n深圳灣24小時通關來港，走佬著草大飛都唔駛"},{"pid":"d940c98c4459be656bab2035b6c916f06e867189","tid":1860872,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:18:55.000Z","msg":"有錢佬唔係可以坐直升機過嚟咩？"},{"pid":"e8ff2c5ba51e359b935bb5fbd9b7f2422f873358","tid":1860872,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d940c98c4459be656bab2035b6c916f06e867189","tid":1860872,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:18:55.000Z","msg":"有錢佬唔係可以坐直升機過嚟咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:23:46.000Z","msg":"連接路起好，去香港機場快過去深圳寶安機場啦"},{"pid":"9b9a38323c4ae96f1c4b4a7abbe4f11f97f2b9c8","tid":1860872,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:29:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"694113b06ee9f8aceb49dae1395fa1841f646844","tid":1860872,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:40:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1b8db71d22805527b9a64ba8eb8758412d605a0b","tid":1860872,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:45:37.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}